'''富氣隕石'''是指含有大量[[非活性氣體|惰性]]氣體，例如[[氦|氦]]、[[氖|氖]]、[[氬|氬]]、[[氪|氪]]、[[氙|氙]]，有時還有其它元素的隕石<ref>{{Cite journal |title=On the origin of gas-rich meteorites |last1=Suess |first1=H. E. |last2=Wänke |first2=H. |date=1964-05-01 |journal=Geochimica et Cosmochimica Acta |volume=28 |issue=5 |publisher=[[ScienceDirect|ScienceDirect]] |pages=595–607 |doi=10.1016/0016-7037(64)90080-8 |last3=Wlotzka |first3=F.|bibcode=1964GeCoA..28..595S }}</ref>。儘管這些氣體實際上幾乎存在所有的隕石中<ref>{{cite book |last1=Swindle |first1=T. |title=Trapped noble gases in meteorites |date=1988 |publisher=University of Arizona Press |location=Tucson |page=535}} in Meteorites and the early solar system, J. F. Kerridge & M. S. Matthews Eds.</ref>，費耶特維爾隕石有〜2,000,000 x10<sup>−8</sup> [[立方公分|cc]][[標準狀況|STP]]/[[克|公克]]氦<ref name="g83">{{cite journal |last1=Goswami |first1=J. |last2=Lal |first2=D. |last3=Wilkening |first3=L. |title=Gas-Rich meteorites: Probes for particle environment and dynamical processes in the inner solar system |journal=Space Science Reviews |date=1983 |volume=37 |issue=1–2 |pages=111–59|bibcode=1984SSRv...37..111G |doi=10.1007/BF00213959 |s2cid=121335431 }}</ref>，或〜2%體積當量的氦。相較[[地球大氣層|背景水準]]是只有幾個[[分率|PPM]]。

富氣隕石的鑑定是依據所存在輕稀有氣體的量，如果不在所有隕石中存在的已知稀有氣體組成分組的基礎上再增加一個分組，就無法解釋其含量<ref name="g83"/>。

== 歷史 ==
[[威廉·拉姆齊|威廉·拉姆齊]]在1895年在地質樣本採樣後不久，在釔鈾礦中第一次發現地球上的氦，而不是通過觀測太陽<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Ramsay |first1=W. |title=Argon and Helium in Meteoritic Iron |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_nature-uk_1895-07-04_52_1340/page/224 |journal=Nature |date=4 Jul 1895 |volume=52 |issue=1340 |pages=224–25 |doi=10.1038/052224a0|bibcode=1895Natur..52..224R |doi-access=free }}</ref>。

鮑爾在1947年提出測定隕石[[放射性定年法|年代]]的方法<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Bauer |first1=C. |title=Production of Helium in Meteorites by Cosmic Radiation |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_physical-review_1947-08-15_72_4/page/354 |journal=Physical Review |date=15 August 1947 |volume=72 |issue=4 |page=354 |doi=10.1103/PhysRev.72.354|bibcode=1947PhRv...72..354B }}</ref>，並由格林（Gerling）和帕夫洛娃（Pavlova）於1951年在出版品上明確的陳述<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Gerling |first1=E. |last2=Pavlova |first2=T. |title=Determination of the geological age of two stony meteorites by the argon method |journal=Doklady Akademii Nauk SSSR |date=1951 |volume=77 |pages=85–97}}</ref>。然而，這很快導致隕石年齡的巨大變化：人們意識到過量的氦（包括氦-3、稀土）也是由輻射產生的<ref name="panethea">{{cite journal |last1=Paneth |first1=F. |last2=Reasbeck |first2=P. |last3=Mayne |first3=K. |title=Production by cosmic rays of helium-3 in meteorites |journal=Nature |date=Aug 1953 |volume=172 |issue=4370 |pages=200–01 |doi=10.1038/172200a0|pmid=13087152 |bibcode=1953Natur.172..200P |s2cid=4149773 }}</ref>。

第一個確認的富氣隕石是由格林和列夫斯基（Levskii）於1956年發表在[[科學雜誌|出版品]]上的斯塔羅佩西亞諾(Staroe Pesyanoe，通常簡稱為Pesyanoe)。與後來的費耶特維爾家族一樣，佩西亞諾的氦含量約為100萬x10<sup>−8</sup> ccSTP/g<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Gerling |first1=E. |last2=Levskii |first2=L. |title=On the origin of the rare gases in stony meteorites |journal=Doklady Akademii Nauk SSR |date=1956 |volume=110 |page=750}}</ref>。

雷諾茲（Reynolds）發表的"一般氙（Xe）的異常"<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Reynolds |first1=J. |title=Xenology |journal=Journal of Geophysical Research |date=15 May 1963 |volume=68 |issue=10 |pages=2939–56 |doi=10.1029/JZ068i010p02939|bibcode=1963JGR....68.2939R }}</ref>，包括Xe<sup>129</sup>等衰變的產物，開創了{{link-en|異種學|xenology}}的子領域<ref>{{cite book |last1=Fleischer |first1=R. |last2=Price |first2=P. |last3=Walker |first3=R. |title=Nuclear Tracks in Solids: Principles and Applications |date=1975 |publisher=University of California Press |chapter=6.5 Study of Nucleosynthesis and the Early History of the Solar System by Extinct Isotopes |isbn=9780520026650 |url-access=registration |url=https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_yfTBvben3GoC }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Hintenberger |first1=H. |title=Xenon in irdischer und in extraterrestrischer Materie (Xenologie) |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_naturwissenschaften_1972-07_59_7/page/285 |journal=Naturwissenschaften |date=Jul 1972 |volume=59 |issue=7 |pages=285–91 |doi=10.1007/BF00593352 |bibcode=1972NW.....59..285H|s2cid=33097923 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Kuroda |first1=P. |title=Xenology: The enigma of xenon in carbonaceous chondrite |journal=Geochemical Journal |date=Jan 1976 |volume=10 |issue=3 |pages=121–36|doi=10.2343/geochemj.10.121|bibcode=1976GeocJ..10..121K |doi-access=free }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Staudacher |first1=T. Allègre C. |title=Terrestrial xenology |journal=Earth and Planetary Science Letters |date=Oct 1982 |volume=60 |issue=3 |pages=389–406 |doi=10.1016/0012-821X(82)90075-9 |bibcode=1982E&PSL..60..389S}}</ref>，一直到今天<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Tolstikhin |first1=I. |last2=Marty |first2=B. |last3=Porcelli |first3=D. |last4=Hofmann |first4=A. |title=Evolution of volatile species in the earth's mantle: A view from xenology |journal=Geochimica et Cosmochimica Acta |date=Jul 2014 |volume=136 |pages=229–46 |doi=10.1016/j.gca.2013.08.034 |bibcode=2014GeCoA.136..229T }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=Diehl |first1=R. |last2=Hartmann |first2=D. |last3=Prantzos |first3=N. |title=Astrophysics with Radioactive Isotopes |date=2018 |publisher=Springer |isbn=978-3319919294 |edition=2nd |chapter=2.2.4 Extinct Radioactivity and Immediate Pre-Solar Nucleosynthesis }}</ref>。

在1980年代首次發表了[[太陽前顆粒|太陽前顆粒]](Presolar grains，PSGs)<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Lewis |first1=R. |last2=Ming |first2=T. |last3=Wacker |first3=J. |last4=Anders |first4=E. |last5=Steel |first5=E. |title=Interstellar diamonds in meteorites |journal=Nature |date=Mar 1987 |volume=326 |issue=6109 |pages=160–62 |doi=10.1038/326160a0|bibcode=1987Natur.326..160L |s2cid=4324489 }}</ref>，這是尋找惰性氣體導出的<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Zinner |first1=E. |last2=Ming |first2=T. |last3=Anders |first3=E. |title=Large isotopic anomalies of Si, C, N and noble gases in interstellar silicon carbide from the Murray meteorite |journal=Nature |date=24 Dec 1987 |volume=330 |issue=6150 |pages=730–32 |doi=10.1038/330730a0|bibcode=1987Natur.330..730Z |s2cid=4306270 }}</ref>；但PSGs並不是單純地通過氣體含量來檢測<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Ott |first1=U. |title=Interstellar grains in meteorites |journal=Nature |date=Jul 1993 |volume=364 |issue=6432 |pages=25–33 |doi=10.1038/364025a0|bibcode=1993Natur.364...25O |s2cid=4271084 }}</ref><ref name="andersMESS"/>。

